# CQ-3: What are all POWL discovery variants and their notation?
PREFIX powl: <urn:ontostar:powl:>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
SELECT ?variant ?label ?notation ?comment WHERE {
  ?variant a powl:DiscoveryVariant ;
           rdfs:label ?label .
  OPTIONAL { ?variant skos:notation ?notation }
  OPTIONAL { ?variant rdfs:comment ?comment }
} ORDER BY ?label
